Module qilletni.api
Package dev.qilletni.api.lang.types

Interface SongType

All Superinterfaces:
AnyType, QilletniType
public non-sealed interface SongType extends AnyType
Represents a song type in Qilletni. This may be created by the "Song Name" by "Artist Name" expression syntax. The internal service provider's type is dynamic, changing how the data is fetched when the service provider is changed.

      SongDefinition getSongDefinition()
      Retrieves the current song definition associated with the implementing object. The song definition determines the method by which song data is classified or resolved, such as by URL, title and artist, or prepopulated data.
      Returns:
      The SongDefinition representing the current song classification method
